{"id":723854331,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 year, 6 months","timestamp":1655402684,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"6 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/723854331/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"7 MB","code":"\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    int myAtoi(string s) {\n        long ans=0;\n        bool positive=1;\n        int i=0,n=s.length(),x=0;\n        while(i<n && s[i]==' ') i++;\n        if(i<n)\n        {\n            if(s[i]=='-')\n            {\n                positive=0;\n                i++;\n            }\n            else if(s[i]=='+')\n                i++;\n            while(i<n && s[i]>='0' && s[i]<='9')\n            {\n                ans=ans*10+s[i]-'0';\n                x = positive ? min((long)INT_MAX,ans) : abs(max((long)INT_MIN,0-ans));\n                if(x!=ans)\n                {\n                    ans=x;\n                    break;\n                }\n                i++;\n            }\n        }\n        return positive? ans:-ans;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
